---
title: Pork Shepherd's Pie with Mangetout and Peas
description: We think that if you can cook a delicious meal without creating mountains of washing up, then you’re on to a winner. This recipe is just that. We’ve given this family favourite a HelloFresh twist by using pork mince instead of beef, and boy is it good. Seasoned with Italian herbs and topped with creamy mash and hard Italian cheese, this recipe is bound to be a hit with the whole family (especially with the washer-uppers!).
